  "title": "Warehouse Storekeeper",
  "description": "<p><strong>HAID BIOTECHNOLOGY INDUSTRY (SINGAPORE) PTE. LTD. </strong>is seeking a detail-oriented and experienced Warehouse Operations Executive<strong> </strong>to join our new startup team in Singapore. The ideal candidate will be overseeing and optimizing the end-to-end warehouse operations, ensuring efficiency, accuracy, and safety in all processes.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>仓库管理员 Warehouse Storekeeper</strong></p><p><strong>一、核心职责 Core Responsibilities</strong></p><ol><li><strong>收货管理 Receiving Management</strong>核对到货数量、包装与单据，执行抽样检查，监督装卸作业，确保货物准确、安全入库。Verify incoming goods against documents for quantity and packaging; conduct sampling checks; supervise loading/unloading to ensure accurate and safe warehousing.</li><li><strong>库存与发货管理 Inventory & Shipping Management</strong>执行先进先出原则，管理仓库储位与日常盘点，确保账、物一致。Implement FIFO principle, manage storage locations and conduct daily counts to ensure system and physical stock alignment.根据销售订单准确备货，监督装车，协调物流，完成发货单据处理。Pick and prepare finished goods accurately per sales orders; supervise loading; coordinate logistics; complete shipping documentation.</li><li><strong>系统操作与数据维护 System Operation & Data Maintenance</strong>及时准确在系统中录入所有出入库、调拨数据，生成相关库存报表。Accurately and promptly record all inbound, outbound, and transfer transactions in the system; generate relevant inventory reports.</li></ol><p><strong>二、主要要求 Key Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>必须有叉车证。</li><li>with forklift certificates.</li><li>可以马上工作者优先</li><li>Able to start immediately or within a short notice period</li><li>1年以上仓库工作经验。</li><li>with 1+ years of warehouse experience.</li><li>熟悉仓库流程，能熟练操作仓库管理系统及办公软件。</li><li>Familiar with warehouse procedures, proficient in using WMS and office software.</li><li>责任心强，注重细节，具备良好的沟通能力和安全意识。</li><li>Strong sense of responsibility, detail-oriented, with good communication skills and safety awareness.</li><li>能适应体力劳动和仓库工作环境。</li><li>Able to handle physical tasks and adapt to a warehouse work environment.</li><li>会讲华语</li><li>Good command of both verbal Mandarin to liaise with Mandarin-speaking business associates.</li></ul>",
